data.description: Bright and updated home in the heart of Hampshire ~ with 3 beds, 2 full baths, and additional finished space in the basement with a closet.  The spacious and sunny four-season room adds a ton of extra living area.  French doors open up to the main living and dining areas, which showcase gorgeous hardwood floors.  There's plenty of storage or work space options with the deep garage and back yard shed, in addition to the full basement. Plus, you'll find the convenience of a first floor bedroom and full bath.  This terrific home is close to downtown, providing convenient access to shops, restaurants, and the library. Additionally, the location offers proximity to parks and schools.
